<body>
<div class="container">
    <center>
        <marquee>
            <h3>Read It Carefully</h3></marquee>
        <p>This Web Application name is: ## Save Course Web APP ##, where you can save or assign your submitted Class Test No. & Title, Assignment No. & Title,
            <br/>
            Lab Report No. & Title on every course of your existing semester.
        </p>
        <p>This web application is developed by
            <h2>Md.Ehsanul Islam Khan.</h2>
        </p>
        <h1>Here some rules of registration system:-</h1>
        <p>
            1. Register User ID with this format: REG***.
            <br/>Don't use any space and any symbolic character( *, ,, ., -, #, $, %, ^, &, !, _ )
        </p>
        <h2>Example: REG001 or Reg001</h2>
        <p>2. Password atleast 6 characters.</p>

        <a href="#" onclick="location.href = '@Url.Action("Register", "CourseDetails")'">Register</a>
    </center>
    <br/><br/><br /><br />
</div>
